# TTA.dev ‚Äî Windsurf Project Rules

## Project Identity

TTA.dev is a **Python library of composable workflow primitives** for building reliable,
observable AI applications. Primitives include retry, timeout, cache, circuit-breaker,
LLM routing, and multi-agent coordination ‚Äî all composable via `>>` and `|` operators.

Repository: https://github.com/theinterneti/TTA.dev

---

## Session Start

Before any non-trivial task:
1. Call `tta_bootstrap` (MCP) for full project orientation
2. Check `TEST_STATUS.md` for current test state
3. Use `codegraphcontext` to orient on code relationships
4. Read `tta://catalog` (MCP resource) for the live primitives catalog
5. Read `tta://patterns` (MCP resource) for detectable workflow patterns

