## ‚õî TODO Format ‚Äî CI-Blocking

**Malformed TODOs block CI.** Required format:

```markdown
- TODO <description> #dev-todo
  type:: <bug|implementation|refactor|documentation>
  priority:: <critical|high|medium|low>
  package:: <package-name>
```

- ‚ùå `# TODO: fix this` ‚Äî BLOCKS CI
- ‚ùå `# FIXME: broken` ‚Äî BLOCKS CI
- ‚úÖ `# TODO fix cache TTL edge case #dev-todo` + properties

